data.description:
This home is like new! 
Built by Richmond American Homes in 2022. 4 bedrooms & 2 full baths, bright and open split floor plan.Tile that looks like wood throughout the living areas.The home backs up to wooded open space, next to Doctors Inlet Elementary School (with private gate access), on a cul-de-sac with sidewalks. Extras include Ring doorbell.rear security camera.indoor motion sensor. AC Nest. Irrigation RACHIO. CAT 5 eithernet in all rooms and patio, 2 in the front room. 
ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE! FHA Mortgage at 4.125%. Buyer would assume the current payoff and pay the difference of the sale price.
